Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.34,0:00:03.48,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,The church?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:09.36,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,Yes. The bandits attempted to raid this wagon\Nfor goods connected to the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.97,0:00:13.86,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,They weren't told what exactly\N they were, however.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.86,0:00:18.87,Default,TSUBAKI,0,0,0,,So they attacked us without knowing \Nwhat they should take?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:24.38,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,They intended to kill the lot of us \Nand make off with all the cargo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.38,0:00:25.62,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,How awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.97,0:00:30.00,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,To appoint the next head,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:33.38,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,the nuns said they needed official \Nauthorization from church HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.38,0:00:36.09,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,Was someone trying to prevent that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:41.47,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,Maybe it's coincidence, but it feels like \Nescorting this wagon was the right choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:15.99,Default,NAKK,0,0,0,,Good work, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.29,0:02:20.49,Default,NAKK,0,0,0,,I made it safely to Bayreun thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.01,0:02:25.37,Default,NAKK,0,0,0,,Here are your certificates of job completion. \NTake these to the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.15,0:02:29.62,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,I'm glad we all made it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:31.72,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yeah. That's what matters most.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:33.00,Default,NAKK,0,0,0,,Absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.44,0:02:36.01,Default,NAKK,0,0,0,,I'll hire you again if I need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.95,0:02:42.26,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Now that we've reported in to the guild,\N what are you two going to do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.82,0:02:45.70,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,We're headed straight to Kilmont.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.70,0:02:46.64,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:49.36,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,We're on our way to Farnid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:50.39,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:54.01,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,I'm sure we'll meet again if it's meant to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.01,0:02:55.94,Default,TSUBAKI,0,0,0,,If you see us, say hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:56.69,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:57.96,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:04.09,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Well, how shall we continue \Nour journey? Another wagon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:06.17,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Do you prefer to travel by wagon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.17,0:03:08.81,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,It {\i1}was{\i0} pretty comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:11.17,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,If a bit painful on the posterior...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.37,0:03:17.25,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Farnid is a pretty long way away.\NThinking ahead, it wouldn't hurt to own one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:19.67,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Okay, let's buy our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.95,0:03:26.93,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,They're all pretty much the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:29.89,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,We'll have to modify one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:33.31,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Hold on. Did I just hear you \Nmake a terrible suggestion?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.97,0:03:35.80,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Whatever do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:37.32,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,You know what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.87,0:03:43.18,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I just want to reduce the shaking \Nand improve the wheel movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:45.26,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,It should make it nicer to ride in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:46.33,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:49.50,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,It won't move without horses \Nor fly through the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:50.33,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I wouldn't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:53.51,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,In other words, you {\i1}could{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.43,0:03:58.01,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Well, as long as it isn't too flashy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.01,0:04:01.47,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,That's the idea.\NI'm still feeling all this out, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:04.58,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,I'd believe that coming from anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.58,0:04:06.97,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Aren't you being mean to me\Nfor no reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.63,0:04:09.72,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,So, which one should we get?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:13.85,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I'd like one large enough to sleep in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:15.85,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:17.86,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,about that size?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:19.36,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:23.40,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,There's room for luggage, and we'll be \Nall set for when my master arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:24.33,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:27.37,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Excuse me! I'd like to buy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:31.12,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,We'll pick it up on our way out of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:32.13,Default,SHOPKEEPER,0,0,0,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:35.37,Default,SHOPKEEPER,0,0,0,,By the way, have you already acquired horses?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:37.41,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.41,0:04:39.13,Default,SHOPKEEPER,0,0,0,,Then I've got a little advice for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:43.52,Default,SHOPKEEPER,0,0,0,,You'll want to get horses \Nwith good legs to pull this wagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:47.01,Default,SHOPKEEPER,0,0,0,,It's a bit too heavy for one horse, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.33,0:04:51.57,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I've heard rumors about people \Nusing monsters to pull their wagons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:55.02,Default,SHOPKEEPER,0,0,0,,Some do. After all, they're way stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.45,0:04:58.26,Default,SHOPKEEPER,0,0,0,,You have to be able to tame one, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.26,0:05:01.03,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I see. Thanks. I'll take that \Ninto consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.81,0:05:07.18,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,We can have Yuzuha transform \Nif we get desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:11.54,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,That's a telepathic call alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:14.29,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,This is Shin. Is that you, Schnee?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:17.98,Italics,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Yes. I've concluded my business \Nin the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:19.17,Italics,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:22.67,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,We just bought a wagon in Bayreun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:26.64,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,After this, we need to find horses\Nto set out for Farnid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:30.63,Italics,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,In that case, allow me to capture \Na monster to pull the wagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.50,0:05:36.09,Italics,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I'll arrive in Bayreun within a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.09,0:05:38.78,Italics,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Could you wait for me there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:41.82,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,Sure. You don't need to rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.14,0:05:46.07,Italics,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Thank you. Also, regarding the Moon Sanctum...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:50.70,Italics,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,The castle was quite concerned\Nover its sudden disappearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.98,0:05:54.70,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,Seriously? They're that worried \Njust because I packed it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:57.40,Italics,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Everyone was rather pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:05:59.64,Italics,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,This will do them good, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:00.83,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:07.04,Italics,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Honestly, I was getting fed up\Nwith their incessant flattery
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:09.50,Italics,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,while trying to observe and recruit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:12.22,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah. That must be rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.63,0:06:14.86,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,I'm sure any kingdom looking
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.86,0:06:18.38,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,to bolster its military \Nwould want you in their ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.38,0:06:22.73,Italics,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Yes. One kingdom even dared to claim \Nownership of the Moon Sanctum.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:26.99,Italics,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I considered eradicating the entire nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:30.01,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,That's no joke coming from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:33.87,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,Maybe they thought they'd get you \Nif they acquired the Moon Sanctum.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:36.58,Italics,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Indeed, there have been people who tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:38.84,Italics,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,And also those who proposed marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:39.87,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yeah, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.26,0:06:45.28,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,I'm the one who made her that way, \Nbut Schnee is a total knockout.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:46.94,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,It's no wonder she's popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:48.38,Italics,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Are you jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:51.03,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:56.77,Italics,SCHEEN,0,0,0,,I see. You're jealous over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:59.30,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,Where did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.30,0:07:00.69,Italics,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:06.33,Italics,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Now then, let me know\Nonce you've found an inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:09.26,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,Sure, you got it. Talk to you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:14.45,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Aren't these pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:19.13,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yeah. It might be nice to wander and \Ntake in the sights while we look for an inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.13,0:07:21.54,Default,WOMAN,0,0,0,,Are you from out of town?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:25.13,Default,WOMAN,0,0,0,,If you haven't found an inn yet, \NI can tell you where's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:29.56,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,This seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:31.41,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:34.57,Default,RECEPTION,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:37.92,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,We're looking for a place to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:40.05,Default,RECEPTION,0,0,0,,Will you be sharing a room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:42.66,Default,BOTH,0,0,0,,S-Separate rooms, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:43.81,Default,RECEPTION,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.22,0:07:46.44,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:51.82,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I can't believe we spent \Nalmost half our reward on an inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:55.82,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,That woman recommended \None heck of a place to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.17,0:07:59.88,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Maybe she thought adventurers could afford it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:04.08,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,It's apparently famous in Bayreun, \Nand it's not bad to indulge once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.93,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,It's definitely a luxury inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:16.09,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,Can I talk now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:19.04,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yeah. It should be fine here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:20.85,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,It's so fluffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.74,0:08:24.56,Main - Top,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,Rolly, rolly! Rolly, rolly! Ack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:24.56,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,We have some time until dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:26.86,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Guess I'll do maintenance on my weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:33.16,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Shin, do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:34.78,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Sure. The door's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:40.25,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Did you tell my master \Nwe're staying in this city?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:40.87,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:45.17,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I don't know exactly when, but she \Nsaid she'd arrive in Bayreun tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:48.48,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,I see. Then we should get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:51.57,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yeah. Let's have dinner in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:56.80,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I'm stuffed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:59.71,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I'll take a quick bath,\Nthen go straight to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:04.02,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,You'll turn into a fox for the night, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:09.40,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Perhaps I'll take a bath and go to bed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.81,0:09:12.12,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,I wanna take a bath together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:13.36,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Sure. That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:15.28,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,Yay! Bath time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:20.28,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,Bath, bath, bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:25.03,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Wait, Yuzuha! We should use the bath in my room...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.61,0:09:32.75,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Guess I'll keep working on my weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:35.05,Main - Top,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,Wow, Tiera! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:37.36,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.36,0:09:38.49,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,They're so soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:40.05,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Yuzuha, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:42.06,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,Hey! I'm right here, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:45.62,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Yuzuha, let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:47.17,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,Boing, boing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:49.06,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:54.99,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,The moon's lovely tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:59.80,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Hey, Yuzuha! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:10.50,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:26.64,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,No wonder I can't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.18,0:10:31.15,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I'm going to work on the wagon \Nuntil Schnee gets here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:32.97,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:36.56,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,I'm curious to see what modifications \Nyou'll make, so maybe I'll watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.56,0:10:37.65,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:44.66,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I should probably start by altering the axles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:51.44,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,If I do this and add some springs, \Nthat should reduce the shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:53.17,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:55.17,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Okay, that should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.10,0:10:59.53,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Now I just need to add the bearings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.21,0:11:02.40,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,What was that, Shin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:04.60,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,The metal went all bendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:07.54,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,It's a creation skill for working metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:09.71,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Though I've adapted it a bit for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:11.44,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,That was fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:12.07,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:16.22,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,That was way too fast!\NIt hasn't even been a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:18.77,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Do modifications always take so little time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:22.45,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Oh, right, we're avoiding attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:26.05,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I'll install the bearings \Nin a more conventional fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.89,0:11:27.76,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.76,0:11:28.70,Italics,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,It's Schnee.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.17,0:11:33.08,Italics,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I've arrived. I'm in the woods \Nbeyond the north gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.85,0:11:36.18,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,Got it. We'll head there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.18,0:11:37.32,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:42.21,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Schnee's here. Let's finish this up \Nand meet her as fast as we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:46.25,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Didn't you just say you'd do the rest normally?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.77,0:11:53.86,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,Something's up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:54.96,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:55.98,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:59.99,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Oh, um... you'll see once we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.67,0:12:02.95,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,We're close.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:04.99,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,Shin, it's strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.99,0:12:16.06,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Huh? What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:23.51,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(320,1)\fnArial\fs10\shad0\bord0\b1\c&HE3E0F3&\pos(81.047,235.524)}Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:23.51,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(320,1)\fnArial\fs12\shad0\bord0\b1\c&HDCEAEC&\pos(201.143,232.476)}Gruefazio Jade
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.26,0:12:19.29,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,A Gruefazio Jade.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:23.51,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,It's a monster whose max level \Nis normally 650.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:29.30,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,But since you don't usually see them with \Nhorns like that, I'm guessing this one's unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.30,0:12:31.02,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I have returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:35.73,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,As promised, I've brought you \Na monster to pull the wagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:40.34,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,This should be able to do the job\Nwithout issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:44.53,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Out of curiosity, where did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:47.58,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,From the nearby sacred mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.58,0:12:50.46,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Always going above and beyond, Schnee...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.46,0:12:52.29,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,You honor me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:55.26,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I mean, it wasn't really a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.26,0:12:59.69,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,She loses all reason when it comes to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:08.18,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,It's already taken a liking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.67,0:13:12.20,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,They're popular with kids, \Nso maybe it's the friendly type.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:14.56,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,This isn't just my problem, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.93,0:13:18.20,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Well, now that we've brought it here, \Nwe're stuck with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:20.08,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Why did you choose this monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:22.57,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,If it is to pull your wagon,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.02,0:13:26.80,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I knew it had to be a monster\Nin the sacred beast class.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:30.04,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Come on, now! It's way too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:32.42,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,What kind of wagon were you \Nexpecting me to get?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:35.62,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I anticipated you would say that, Shin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:36.53,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:40.59,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Go on. Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:54.18,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,It shrank?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:56.98,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,So it has that ability, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.53,0:14:00.26,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,It can go even smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:02.48,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,It will be quite convenient \Nfor staying at inns.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:05.87,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,You're right. This size should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:08.51,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,I'm strangely exhausted...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:13.99,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,It was intimidating enough before\Nto make most people faint.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:15.43,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:19.88,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,You're both crazy for carrying on\Nlike it was no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:24.75,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Still, I never expected her \Nto bring something so high-level.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:27.28,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:32.42,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Master! Most people wouldn't even think\Nof making a sacred beast pull a wagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:35.34,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Do you not like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.34,0:14:36.02,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:40.54,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Wait, wait! Why are you getting sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:42.06,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I don't have a problem with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:45.67,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I'm happy to have a cool \Nsacred beast pull my wagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.21,0:14:57.16,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,He says, "You can count on me."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:15:00.34,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,You two monsters \Ncan communicate with each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:02.31,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,He really is a sacred beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:10.01,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,By the way, what's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:11.66,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,His name is Shimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:15.26,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,He can use illusion and thunder skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:18.87,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Shimmer, huh? Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:22.57,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Mind your manners around my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.86,0:15:29.07,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Okay, Shimmer. Our first destination is Farnid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.77,0:15:34.16,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,We're going to see an old friend named Girart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:37.55,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,So let's go! Take us to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.31,0:15:44.54,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,This is great! It feels amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:54.43,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I guess we're still drawing attention, \Ndespite my best efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:57.49,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Well, there's nothing we can do about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:15:58.92,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,It really is incredible, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.92,0:16:01.81,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,The wagon doesn't shake at all, \Nand my rear doesn't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.34,0:16:05.41,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,It outperforms even a royal carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.41,0:16:09.94,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I've ridden in one before, \Nand it wasn't this comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:19.01,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.01,0:16:20.95,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,Shimmer's childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.43,0:16:25.46,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,Shimmer and his mom used to rule \Nthe sacred mountain together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.89,0:16:30.63,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,But an adventurer defeated his mom, \Nand only Shimmer survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:33.10,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,An adventurer, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.07,0:16:38.47,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,I'm ashamed to admit \NI did similar things in the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:42.98,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,He ran as fast as he could \Nand was rescued by an elf girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:48.06,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,Then he worked hard to get stronger \Nand return to the sacred mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.58,0:16:50.59,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,An elf, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.59,0:16:53.99,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,No wonder he wasn't \Nespecially cautious around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:17:02.01,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,He says he followed you \Nbecause you smelled familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:03.99,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:07.38,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,He says it was Tiera's smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:09.00,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:13.01,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Was Tiera the elf girl who rescued you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:15.54,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.54,0:17:16.51,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:19.26,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.05,0:17:24.17,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,I did save an injured puppy when I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:27.60,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,I thought they looked similar, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:29.29,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Could it really be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:33.04,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,He says you met over a century ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.04,0:17:37.36,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Then it is him! I see... So you're that puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:43.52,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Then why don't I transfer ownership\Nof Shimmer to you, Tiera?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:44.50,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:46.86,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Will that be okay at her level?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:50.13,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,There should be no problem \Nif both parties accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:54.79,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I shall dissolve our contract \Nand have you form a new one with Tiera.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.94,0:18:02.26,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,First, to dissolve the contract...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:08.77,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,May there be light where you walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.73,0:18:20.78,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Okay, Tiera, you're next.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.42,0:18:22.22,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:36.42,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,It's okay. I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.96,0:18:45.34,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,It is my desire to walk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:04.58,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Whoa, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:06.58,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.73,0:19:10.81,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Sorry. I suddenly felt weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.33,0:19:16.26,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,I'm fine. I just need to rest a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:24.35,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Hey, Schnee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:29.08,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Did you let Tiera have Shimmer \Nso he could protect her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:30.35,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Yes, precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:34.01,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,We can't always be by her side,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.58,0:19:40.88,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,and I'd feel better knowing Shimmer is \Nwith her when she chooses her own path.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:44.97,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Now that they've formed an ownership \Ncontract, she can summon Shimmer anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:45.87,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,We can count on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:50.30,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I'd come running anytime you're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.90,0:19:52.50,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.34,0:19:57.50,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Honestly, you're the one I turn \Nto when I'm really screwed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.41,0:19:59.51,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.33,0:20:05.48,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Schnee?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.48,0:20:06.82,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,You can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.82,0:20:07.40,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:09.77,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:11.64,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.43,0:20:19.53,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,This forest goes on forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:22.88,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,We're in southeastern Farnid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:25.91,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,It's right on the edge of Raluah Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:30.04,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Someone's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:32.52,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,They're pretty high-level.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:36.33,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I just sent a message to Girart.\NThey must be here to meet us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.31,0:20:43.05,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I thought you might come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:50.73,Default,WOLFGANG,0,0,0,,We came on orders of the First King.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.73,0:20:51.86,Default,WOLFGANG,0,0,0,,Are they the ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:55.94,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Yes. Please take us to Girart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:20:59.44,Default,WOLFGANG,0,0,0,,Very well. We'll show you to the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.26,0:21:15.59,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Hey, do you know those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:18.42,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,They're Girart's grandchildren.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:19.21,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:39.18,Default,QUORE,0,0,0,,We've brought Schnee's party.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.18,0:21:40.47,Default,GIRART,0,0,0,,Enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.45,0:22:03.98,Default,GIRART,0,0,0,,Hey, Master. I didn't think I'd get \Nto see you again in this life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:40.02,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs20\b1\c&HBCE7FD&\3c&H192541&\shad0}Next Time\NEpisode 8\N{\fs24\b1\fscy130\fsp1\c&HB8E7FF&\bord0\shad0}Trusted and Entrusted
